es-only story\n- Coverage: 97.09% overall, all 152 files above 80% floor\n\n### 13-1-agentdriver-interface-and-types — verification (2026-03-24T19:44:00Z)\n\n- Precondition failed: AGENTS.md staleness for `src/lib/__tests__/fixtures` — checker falls back to root AGENTS.md instead of `src/lib/AGENTS.md`\n- Fixed by creating `src/lib/__tests__/fixtures/AGENTS.md` — workaround for fallback logic gap in `checkAgentsMdForModule`\n- All 10 ACs passed unit-testable verification with direct CLI checks\n- Beads sync failed — story file status line not found (likely a parsing issue)\n\n### 13-2-ralph-driver-implementation — create-story (2026-03-24T19:50:00Z)\n\n- Expanded from 2 epic-level ACs to 16 detailed ACs based on codebase analysis\n- Ambiguity: `createLineProcessor` ownership — epic says delete `run-helpers.ts` but non-ralph functions live there; scoped to migrate ralph-specific only\n- Ambiguity: `AgentEvent.retry` expects `{ attempt, delay }` but ralph stderr doesn't include delay info — type may need relaxing\n- Risk: `run.ts` re-exports `buildSpawnArgs` from `run-helpers.ts` — migration will break re-export chain\n- Risk: Moving `stream-parser.ts` changes public API import path in `src/index.ts`\n- All 16 ACs tagged cli-verifiable — no integration-required needed\n\n### 13-2-ralph-driver-implementation — dev-story (2026-03-24T20:00:00Z)\n\n- Pre-existing ~80 TS type errors in test files (unrelated to this story, all in mocks with incomplete type annotations)\n- `RalphDriver.spawn()` hardcodes defaults (maxIterations: 50, iterationTimeout: 30, calls: 100) — SpawnOpts doesn't carry ralph-specific options; deferred to 13-3\n- `resolveRalphPath()` path calculation changed due to deeper directory nesting — adjusted relative traversal\n- `parseOutput()` maps retry events with `delay: 0` — ralph stderr doesn't include delay info; stream-json events have real delay\n- All 307 BATS + 3600 vitest tests pass with zero regressions\n\n### 13-2-ralph-driver-implementation — code-review (2026-03-24T20:10:00Z)\n\n- HIGH (fixed): `tool-complete` AgentEvent emitted fabricated empty `name`/`args` strings — types.ts updated to make them optional\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Zero test coverage for `RalphDriver.spawn()` method — added 5 tests\n- MEDIUM (fixed): No tool-complete delegation test — added 1 test\n- LOW (unfixed): `spawn()` hardcodes maxIterations/iterationTimeout/calls — SpawnOpts needs expansion in 13-3\n- LOW (unfixed): `resolveRalphPath()` uses fragile `endsWith('/src')` check\n- LOW (unfixed): `retry` event drops story key — AgentEvent.retry has no `key` field\n- Architecture: `createLineProcessor` in run-helpers.ts imports from agents/ralph.ts — reverse dependency to resolve in 13-3\n- Coverage: 97.08% overall, all 153 files above 80% floor\n\n### 13-3-migrate-run-ts-to-agentdriver — create-story (2026-03-24T20:17:00Z)\n\n- Ambiguity: Epic AC references `driver.getExecutablePath()` but AgentDriver has no such method — path encapsulated in `spawn()`\n- SpawnOpts mismatch: Interface has 5 fields, run.ts needs 10+ — requires constructor-time config pattern\n- RalphDriver.spawn() hardcodes values from 13-2 that must be made configurable first\n- createLineProcessor disposition unclear — possibly remove after migration\n- Re-export breakage risk: run.ts re-exports buildSpawnArgs/resolveRalphPath that external consumers may use\n\n### 13-3-migrate-run-ts-to-agentdriver — dev-story (2026-03-24T20:25:00Z)\n\n- AgentEvent-to-StreamEvent type cast in handleAgentEvent — shapes match structurally but no formal type relationship\n- createLineProcessor still exists in run-helpers.ts, unused by run.ts, imports from agents/ralph.js — cleanup candidate\n- Single line handler for both stdout/stderr — correct but stdout lines get unnecessary ralph message pattern checks\n- storyKey: '' passed to driver.spawn() — SpawnOpts requires it but run.ts doesn't have a single story key\n","numLines":183,"startLine":1,"totalLines":183}}}
